#. type: Table
#: _generated-doc/main/config/quarkus-aesh.adoc
msgid ""
"icon:lock[title=Fixed at build time] [[quarkus-aesh_quarkus-aesh-mode]] [.property-path]##link:#quarkus-aesh_quarkus-aesh-mode[`+++quarkus.aesh.mode+++`]##\n"
"config_property_copy_button:+++quarkus.aesh.mode+++[]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"[.description]\n"
"--\n"
"The execution mode for the Aesh extension.\n"
"\n"
" * `auto` - Automatically detect the mode based on annotations. Uses runtime mode for single command or group commands, console mode for multiple commands.\n"
" * `runtime` - Use AeshRuntimeRunner for single command execution (like picocli).\n"
" * `console` - Use AeshConsoleRunner for interactive shell mode.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Environment variable: env_var_with_copy_button:+++QUARKUS_AESH_MODE+++[]\n"
"--"
msgstr ""

#. type: Table
